ed="T" n="0738a22"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0738a22"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042216">京師西明寺</placeName><persName key="A001729">慧琳</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0738a23"/><persName key="A001729">釋慧琳</persName>、姓裴氏，<placeName key="PL000000047892">疎勒國</placeName>人也。始事<persName key="A000095">不空三<lb
ed="T" n="0738a24"/>藏</persName>，為室灑，內持密藏，外究儒流，<placeName key="PL000000048207">印度</placeName>聲明<ptr target="#n88"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0738a25"/><placeName key="PL000000000083">支那</placeName>詁訓，靡不精奧。甞謂翻梵成華，華皆<lb
ed="T" n="0738a26"/>典故，典故則<placeName key="PL000000048207">西乾</placeName>細語也。遂引用《字林》、《字統》、<lb
ed="T" n="0738a27"/>《聲類》、《三蒼》<ptr target="#n818"/>、《切韻》、《玉篇》、諸經雜史，參合佛意，詳<lb
ed="T" n="0738a28"/>察是非，撰成《大藏音義》一百卷。起<date from-iso="0788-02-16" key="j20089172017302" to-iso="0811-01-31">貞元四年<lb
ed="T" n="0738a29"/>迄元和五載</date>，方得絕筆<ptr target="#n14"/>，貯其本于<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明</placeName>藏<pb ed="T" n="0738b" xml:id="T50.2061.0738b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0738b01"/>中。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>之間，一皆宗仰。<persName key="A001729">琳</persName>以<date from-iso="0820-01-23" key="j20205812020967" to-iso="0821-02-12">元和十五年庚<lb
ed="T" n="0738b02"/>子</date>卒於所住，春秋八十四矣。殆<date from-iso="0851-02-09" key="j20319212032274" to-iso="0852-01-28">大中五年</date>，有<lb
ed="T" n="0738b03"/>奏請入藏流行。近以海中<placeName key="PL000000048554">高麗國</placeName>，雖<placeName key="PL000000048607">三韓</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0738b04"/>夷族，偏尚釋門，<date from-iso="0954" key="j20695432071729" to-iso="0960">周顯德中</date>，遣使齎金入<placeName key="PL000000008355">浙</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0738b05"/>中求<persName key="A001729">慧琳</persName>《經音義》，時無此本，故有闕如。</p>
